2017年1月1日约1:30（[[UTC+3|UTC+3]]），在伊斯坦布尔[[贝西克塔什|贝西克塔什]][[奥塔科伊|奥塔科伊]]的雷纳夜总会发生的大规模枪击事件，致至少39人死亡，69人在袭击中受伤。<ref name="cumhuriyet"/><ref name="#1">{{cite web|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-europe-38481521|title=Istanbul nightclub attack 'leaves 35 dead'|date=1 January 2017|publisher=|accessdate=1 January 2017|via=www.bbc.co.uk|archive-date=2017-01-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170101031150/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-europe-38481521|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="#2">{{cite web|url=http://www.euronews.com/2017/01/01/several-people-wounded-in-an-attack-on-a-nightclub-in-istanbul-two-attackers-involved-turkish-ntv-television|title=At least 35 shot dead in Istanbul 'terror attack'|date=1 January 2017|work=euronews.com|accessdate=1 January 2017|archive-date=2019-09-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190912125922/https://www.euronews.com/2017/01/01/several-people-wounded-in-an-attack-on-a-nightclub-in-istanbul-two-attackers|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="independent">{{cite web|last1=Griffien|first1=Andrew|title=Istanbul nightclub attack: Several injured after gunman opens fire on New Year's Eve|url=http://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/europe/istanbul-nightclub-attack-shooting-turkey-gunman-injured-killed-victims-new-years-eve-2016-2017-a7504046.html|website=independent.co.uk|publisher=The Independent|accessdate=January 1, 2017|archive-date=2019-04-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190428155743/https://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/europe/istanbul-nightclub-attack-shooting-turkey-gunman-injured-killed-victims-new-years-eve-2016-2017-a7504046.html|dead-url=no}}</ref> 当时有数百人在此地庆祝新年。

== 背景 ==
因近几个月以来，接连发生的数起由[[伊斯兰国|伊斯兰国]]和[[伊拉克库尔德斯坦|库尔德]]武装发动的恐怖袭击对土耳其造成了严重影响<ref name="BBC">{{cite news|title=Istanbul Reina nightclub attack 'leaves 39 dead'|url=http://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-38481521|accessdate=1 January 2017|work=BBC News|agency=BBC|date=1 January 2017|archive-date=2019-05-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190528141530/https://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-38481521|dead-url=no}}</ref>，本次事件发生当天伊斯坦布尔全城处于高度戒备状态，有17000名警察在执勤<ref name="Bilginsoy">{{cite web | last=Bilginsoy | first=Zeynep | title=2 reported dead in New Year's attack on Istanbul nightclub | website=AP News | url=https://apnews.com/643830e3d74f4c668ac19b177126d862/Several-wounded-in-New-Year%27s-attack-on-Istanbul-night-club | accessdate=1 January 2017 | archive-date=2017-01-01 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170101091541/https://apnews.com/643830e3d74f4c668ac19b177126d862/Several-wounded-in-New-Year%27s-attack-on-Istanbul-night-club | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2016年12月17日在土耳其中部城市[[凯塞里|凯塞里]]，汽车炸弹导致14名军人牺牲，数十人受伤，其中大多是军人<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.trt.net.tr/chinese/tu-er-qi/2017/01/04/kai-sai-li-bao-zha-an-zhen-po-qu-de-jin-zhan-ming-nu-xian-fan-bei-bu-644399 |title=凯塞里爆炸案侦破取得进展 一名女嫌犯被捕 |accessdate=2017-01-05 |archive-date=2017-01-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170106010428/http://www.trt.net.tr/chinese/tu-er-qi/2017/01/04/kai-sai-li-bao-zha-an-zhen-po-qu-de-jin-zhan-ming-nu-xian-fan-bei-bu-644399 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 袭击 ==
据报导，一个身着[[圣诞老人|圣诞老人]]服饰的枪手，在凌晨1:15左右向夜总会里开火。他携带[[卡拉什尼科夫自動步槍|AK-47]]，在杀死门口的一个警察和旁观者后进入夜总会。<ref name="AA-31-12-16">{{cite web|title=35 killed in armed attack at Istanbul nightclub|url=http://aa.com.tr/en/turkey/35-killed-in-armed-attack-at-istanbul-nightclub/717919|website=aa.com.tr|publisher=Anadolu Agency|accessdate=31 December 2016|archive-date=2017-01-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170102172915/http://aa.com.tr/en/turkey/39-killed-in-terror-attack-at-istanbul-nightclub/717919|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="hurriyet">{{cite web|title=Son Dakika: Ünlü gece kulübüne silahlı saldırı|url=http://www.hurriyet.com.tr/son-dakika-unlu-gece-kulubune-silahli-saldiri-40323300|publisher=Hürriyet|accessdate=31 December 2016|archive-date=2019-09-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190912125922/http://www.hurriyet.com.tr/gundem/son-dakika-reinada-silahli-saldiri-40323300|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="reuters">{{cite web|title=One attacker still inside Istanbul nightclub: CNN Turk|url=http://www.reuters.com/article/us-turkey-attack-idUSKBN14K0NH|website=reuters.com|publisher=Reuters|accessdate=1 January 2017|archive-date=2017-01-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170101043257/http://www.reuters.com/article/us-turkey-attack-idUSKBN14K0NH|dead-url=no}}</ref>据悉枪手本人讲阿拉伯语<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.sondakika.com/haber/haber-istanbul-da-gece-kulubune-saldiri-cok-sayida-9119548/|title=Gece Kulübü Reina’ya Terör Saldırısı Vali Şahin: 1 Polis Şehit, 35 Sivil Hayatını Kaybetti|work=sondakika.com|accessdate=1 January 2017|archive-date=2017-01-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170101161200/http://www.sondakika.com/haber/haber-istanbul-da-gece-kulubune-saldiri-cok-sayida-9119548/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，他本人仍然在逃。<ref name="auto1">{{cite web|url=https://www.theguardian.com/world/live/2017/jan/01/istanbul-nightclub-attack-dozens-killed-new-years-eve-mass-shooting-live-updates|title=Istanbul nightclub attack: 16 foreigners among 39 killed, says minister – live updates|first=Graham|last=Russell|date=1 January 2017|publisher=|accessdate=1 January 2017|via=The Guardian|archive-date=2017-01-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170101123111/https://www.theguardian.com/world/live/2017/jan/01/istanbul-nightclub-attack-dozens-killed-new-years-eve-mass-shooting-live-updates|dead-url=no}}</ref> 政府部门早些时候称一个枪手在进入夜总会后不久被警察击毙，与此同时，一些袭击目击者向土耳其媒体透露本次袭击不止有一个袭击者参与。<ref name="TG">{{cite news|last1=Shaheen|first1=Kareem|title=Turkey nightclub shooting: Istanbul on alert after armed gunman kills dozens|url=https://www.theguardian.com/world/2016/dec/31/turkey-armed-attacker-opens-fire-in-istanbul-nightclub-reports|accessdate=1 January 2017|work=The Guardian|agency=The Guardian|date=1 January 2017|archive-date=2017-02-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170208235653/https://www.theguardian.com/world/2016/dec/31/turkey-armed-attacker-opens-fire-in-istanbul-nightclub-reports|dead-url=no}}</ref>土耳其政府部门因为安全和公共秩序方面的疑虑，已经下达了对于此事的临时媒体管制命令。<ref name="BBC" />

在袭击发生的那刻，大约有700人正在夜总会里庆祝新年。<ref name="cumhuriyet">{{cite web|title=İstanbul'da Reina gece kulübünde silahlı saldırı: 2 ölü, çok sayıda yaralı var|url=http://www.cumhuriyet.com.tr/haber/turkiye/653641/istanbul_da_Reina_gece_kulubunde_silahli_saldiri__2_olu__cok_sayida_yarali_var.html|publisher=Cumhuriyet|accessdate=1 January 2017|archive-date=2019-09-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190912125923/http://www.cumhuriyet.com.tr/haber/turkiye/653641/Reina_da_katliam..._istanbul_da_eglence_merkezine_silahli_saldiri__1_i_polis_39_olu__65_yarali.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="BBC" />其中，至少39人死亡<ref name="#1"/><ref name="#2"/><ref name="independent"/>（包括15名外国人）<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nbc12.com/story/34160467/the-latest-turkey-lowers-number-of-foreign-fatalities|title=The Latest: Turkey lowers number of foreign fatalities|work=nbc12.com|accessdate=1 January 2017|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170102080305/http://www.nbc12.com/story/34160467/the-latest-turkey-lowers-number-of-foreign-fatalities|archivedate=2017年1月2日}}</ref>以及至少69人受伤。<ref name="auto">{{cite web|title=Istanbul nightclub attack: At least 35 dead after gunmen open fire at New Year's Eve party|url=http://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/europe/istanbul-nightclub-attack-shooting-turkey-gunman-injured-killed-victims-new-years-eve-2016-2017-a7504046.html|accessdate=1 January 2017|archive-date=2019-04-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190428155743/https://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/europe/istanbul-nightclub-attack-shooting-turkey-gunman-injured-killed-victims-new-years-eve-2016-2017-a7504046.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>警方已经在夜总会周围设置了警戒线。<ref name="Graham 2016">{{cite web | last=Graham | first=Chris | title=Istanbul attack: Gunmen 'dressed as Santa' open fire at nightclub in Turkey | website=The Telegraph | date=31 December 2016 | url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/2016/12/31/istanbul-attack-gunmen-dressed-santa-open-fire-nightclub-turkey/ | accessdate=1 January 2017 | archive-date=2017-01-01 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170101013946/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/2016/12/31/istanbul-attack-gunmen-dressed-santa-open-fire-nightclub-turkey/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>有一些人跳入了[[伊斯坦布尔海峡|伊斯坦布尔海峡]]以躲避袭击。<ref name="ht">{{cite web|title=İstanbul'da gece kulübünde silahlı saldırı|url=http://www.haberturk.com/gundem/haber/1343321-istanbulda-gece-kulubune-silahli-saldiri|publisher=Habertürk|accessdate=31 December 2016|archive-date=2017-01-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170101085301/http://www.haberturk.com/gundem/haber/1343321-istanbulda-gece-kulubune-silahli-saldiri|dead-url=no}}</ref>

[[伊斯坦布尔省|伊斯坦布尔省]]省长 {{link-en|Vasip Sahin|Vasip Sahin}} 表示这是一起恐怖袭击事件。<ref name="euronews 2017">{{cite web | title=At least 35 shot dead in Istanbul 'terror attack' | website=euronews | date=1 January 2017 | url=http://www.euronews.com/2017/01/01/several-people-wounded-in-an-attack-on-a-nightclub-in-istanbul-two-attackers-involved-turkish-ntv-television | accessdate=1 January 2017 | archive-date=2019-09-12 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190912125922/https://www.euronews.com/2017/01/01/several-people-wounded-in-an-attack-on-a-nightclub-in-istanbul-two-attackers | dead-url=no }}</ref>据报导，从袭击发生的时间和袭击对象考虑，安保部门暗示[[伊斯兰国|伊斯兰国]]参与了这起恐怖袭击。<ref name="Graham 2016"/>

